      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830439,
      "updated": 1775880747
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905a400000000000bf4b7",
      "text": "[未解決謎解き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830439,
      "updated": 1775880759
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905a400000000000bf4b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775830439,
      "updated": 1775874796
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905a400000000000bf4b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830439,
      "updated": 1775830439
    },
    {
      "id": "69d904b600000000000bf486",
      "text": ">[funadeni https://x.com/funadeni/status/2039908498042126820] 【X限定謎解き】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830201,
      "updated": 1775830219
    },
    {
      "id": "69d904c800000000000bf488",
      "text": "> 答えが見える異能を駆使して、全ての謎を解き明かせ！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830219,
      "updated": 1775830219
    },
    {
      "id": "69d904c800000000000bf489",
      "text": "> #春から未来大",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830219,
      "updated": 1775830219
    },
    {
      "id": "69d904c800000000000bf48a",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE8dBL3awAA8qK1?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830219,
      "updated": 1775830219
    },
    {
      "id": "69d904c800000000000bf48b",
      "text": "\t[~ 2時から5時を繋ごうとして虹とゴジラを繋いだら「ちがうよ」になって、ちがうのか〜となってからどうしたらいいかわからない][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830219,
      "updated": 1775830279
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9050400000000000bf4b4",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 1が「いただきます」で「いま」だとして、それを赤四角に入れる。これを通って意味がありそうな文章は「あかるいまっちさき」だが、それで何？となっている]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830279,
      "updated": 1775830387
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9058600000000000bf4b5",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 「読め」ではなく「読ぬ」になってるのも気になる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830408,
      "updated": 1775830436
    },
    {
      "id": "69dab35200000000003e6e49",
      "text": "\t\t [~ 誤字だ][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775940434,
      "updated": 1775940568
    },
    {
      "id": "69de4e5e00000000000cdeda",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 2個目の画像で色々やってたらマッチのとこから2時方向に行って5時方向に行くと「ほそじ」になり、次の謎の指示の意味が通ることに気づいた][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776176735,
      "updated": 1776176811
    },
    {
      "id": "69de4f2400000000000cdedb",
      "text": "\t\t最後のがわからない[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776176933,
      "updated": 1776176938
    },
    {
      "id": "69de55d50000000000e5447a",
      "text": "\t\t [~ 今までに得られたキーワードを入れて緑の枠の位置で横に読むとそれっぽい単語になった][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776178644,
      "updated": 1776178720
    },
    {
      "id": "69de5adc00000000004ba2ef",
      "text": "\t\t ほんとだ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776179932,
      "updated": 1776179936
    },
    {
      "id": "69de6cca0000000000e5447e",
      "text": "\t\t [~ でも緑の枠の具現化を考える必要があるのか 今ひとつしっくりこない][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776184520,
      "updated": 1776184598
    },
    {
      "id": "69de561b0000000000e5447b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776178713,
      "updated": 1776178713
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90b1800000000000bf5a4",
      "text": ">[utsuronamame https://x.com/utsuronamame/status/2041800716264861900] 本日の謎解きです!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775831832,
      "updated": 1775831832
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90b1800000000000bf5a5",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HDW_QLCbMAA9cNZ?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775831832,
      "updated": 1775831832
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90b1800000000000bf5a6",
      "text": "\tこの人と相性悪いのか他のも含めて全然わかんないんだよな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775831832,
      "updated": 1775831858
    },
    {
      "id": "69dab53d00000000003e6e4a",
      "text": "\t[~ この記号は…なるほどw][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775940926,
      "updated": 1775940942
    },
    {
      "id": "69de48d100000000000cded6",
      "text": "\t なるほどw[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
