      "created": 1775830672,
      "updated": 1775830672
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9068d00000000000bf4bb",
      "text": ">[sknkn_skndY https://x.com/sknkn_skndY/status/2039976202325147956] 白い図形の形は多分なんでしょう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830672,
      "updated": 1775830673
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9068e00000000000bf4bc",
      "text": "> #この謎には白い図形が含まれます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830673,
      "updated": 1775830673
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9068e00000000000bf4bd",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9guLraYAAfeV1?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830673,
      "updated": 1775830673
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9068e00000000000bf4be",
      "text": "\t[~ ようがん、たぬき、ひがし][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830673,
      "updated": 1775830698
    },
    {
      "id": "69d906a700000000000bf4ef",
      "text": "\t\t[~ さようたたかったひろ→(たぬき)→さようかっひろ→(ようがん)→さんかっひろ→(ひがし)→さんかっしろ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830698,
      "updated": 1775830783
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9070c00000000000bf4f0",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 白い図形が入って「しろいずけい」「しろ is けい」で　さんかっしろ→さんかっけい　となる]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830799,
      "updated": 1775830847
